<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.3.6">
<l>añcuṭa rāḻiyuṉ kaiyakat tēntum aḻakānī poykai pukku</l>
<l>nañcumiḻ nākatti ṉōṭu piṇaṅkavum nāṉuyir vāḻnti runtēṉ</l>
<l>eṉceyya veṉṉai vayiṟu maṟukkiṉā yētumō racca millai</l>
<l>kañcaṉ maṉattuk kukappaṉa vēceytāy kāyāmpū vaṇṇam koṇṭāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Beauty who holds the fine fiery discus in the palm [of your hands]!</l>
<l>I went on living [my] life</l>
<l rend="indent">even though you fought the venom spitting snake in that pond.</l>
<l>What [am I] to do? You make my stomach hurt!</l>
<l rend="indent">You fear nothing at all.</l>
<l>The things you did were a pleasure to the mind of Kaṃsa,</l>
<l>Oh you who took the colour of the Kāyā flower!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
